{"title":"【066】字体和字号","slug":"hell0-world14","date":"2022-10-02T02:33:59.000Z","updated":"2023-06-21T11:17:03.464Z","comments":true,"path":"api/articles/hell0-world14.json","photos":[],"link":"","excerpt":"                font family&size                       font-family:字体。","covers":null,"content":"<!DOCTYPE html>\n<html lang=\"en\">\n<head>\n    <meta charset=\"UTF-8\">\n    <meta http-equiv=\"X-UA-Compatible\" content=\"IE=edge\">\n    <meta name=\"viewport\" content=\"width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0\">\n    <title>font family&size</title>\n    <link rel=\"stylesheet\" href=\"./mystyle1.css\">  \n</head>\n<body>\n    <h1></h1>\n    <p class=\"wb\"> \n        font-family:字体。<span id=\"more\"></span>名称：serif(优雅),sans-serif（圆直）如helvetica,monospace（等宽）,cursive（首先）,fantasy（装饰，娱乐）\n    </p>\n    <p>\n        中文字体：微软雅黑，苹方简，其它字体看自己是否安装。在电脑外观-字体，可查看。\n    </p>\n    <p class=\"sb\">\n        如果访客没有该字体，可以多备用在前添加几种，分别引号引用逗号隔开。<br><br>\n        先定义的字体优先使用，如果没有就使用默认字体<br><br>\n        字号：font-size,值为几px,或几em(16px)/百分数，默认字号为16px。<br><br>\n    </p>\n</body>\n</html>","categories":[{"name":"CSS","slug":"CSS","count":30,"path":"api/categories/CSS.json"}],"tags":[]}